🔹 1. Signup Flow

🧾 Step-by-step

1. User form fill karta hai
Email + Password

2. Button click → fetch call
fetch("/api/auth/signup", {...})

3. API hit hota hai
/app/api/auth/signup/route.js

4. Backend kya karta hai?
Data read (req.json())
User save karta hai

5. Response aata hai
User created

